IFDHandler for a serial port connected board running FlexCOS. This is basicall a userspace driver for PCSC-Lite on Linux that enables software using the PCSC-Lite deamon to communicate with FlexCOS.

For more information see the FlexCOS wiki at:

https://github.com/FlexCOS/lib-tty-ifdhandler/wiki

